data.description: Welcome to 4380 Ivy Run, a truly magnificent home that offers an expansive living experience in the serene community of Holly Hill. This impressive house boasts 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and spacious parking for 2 vehicles. Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of space and natural light that fills every corner of this stunning property. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between rooms, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. Large windows adorn the walls, allowing sunlight to bathe the interiors in warmth and creating an inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek stainless steel appliances that add a touch of modern elegance. With over 10-foot ceilings, the living room exudes grandeur and coziness simultaneously. Picture yourself curling up by the fireplace on chilly winter nights, creating memories that will last a lifetime. For those who love to host dinner parties or enjoy family meals together, the separate dining room provides an ideal setting. With enough space to accommodate a large dining table, you can gather your loved ones and indulge in delicious meals while creating cherished moments. Retreat to the spacious bedrooms, each offering walk-in closets that provide ample storage space for your personal belongings. The master bedroom is a sanctuary in itself, complete with a separate shower and soaking tub where you can relax and unwind after a long day. Outside, the vast yard beckons you to enjoy the great outdoors. Whether it's hosting barbecues, playing games with family and friends, or simply basking in the sun's warmth, this outdoor oasis offers endless possibilities for relaxation and recreation. Conveniently located near the freeway, this home provides easy access to downtown Atlanta within approximately 15 minutes and Hartsfield Airport in about 25 minutes. You'll have all the convenience of city living while enjoying the tranquility of Holly Hill.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a spacious, light-filled home in a peaceful community. Schedule your private viewing today and discover the lifestyle that awaits you at 4380 Ivy Run. **Please bare with us while the seller continues to renovate and begin the moving process, dumpster in driveway**
